djdj
kk
ng
nj
rd
rdd
rl
rn
rr




!! used to control hyphenation
вҲ‘ !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = trigger for hyphen that does not work like hyphenation

!! ## Flag diacritics
!! We have manually optimised the structure of our lexicon using following
!! flag diacritics to restrict morhpological combinatorics - only allow compounds
!! with verbs if the verb is further derived into a noun again:
!!
!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | ---- | -----------
@P.NeedNoun.ON@    !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised
@D.NeedNoun.ON@    !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised
@C.NeedNoun@       !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised

!! Following flags are used to control tokenisation and analyses in certain
!! corner cases (e.g. a full stop at the end of the sentence is also needed for
!! a full stop of an abbreviation).

!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | ---- | -----------
@P.Pmatch.Loc@       !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | split point for multitoken word
@P.Pmatch.Backtrack@ !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | merge point for mutltiword token
!! 
!! For languages that allow compounding, the following flag diacritics are needed
!! to control position-based compounding restrictions for nominals. Their use is
!! handled automatically if combined with +CmpN/xxx tags. If not used, they will
!! do no harm.
!!
!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | ---- | -----------
@P.CmpFrst.FALSE@ !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Require that words tagged as such only appear first
@D.CmpPref.TRUE@  !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Block such words from entering ENDLEX
@P.CmpPref.FALSE@ !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Block these words from making further compounds
@D.CmpLast.TRUE@  !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Block such words from entering R
@D.CmpNone.TRUE@  !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Combines with the next tag to prohibit compounding
@U.CmpNone.FALSE@ !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Combines with the prev tag to prohibit compounding
@P.CmpOnly.TRUE@  !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Sets a flag to indicate that the word has passed R
@D.CmpOnly.FALSE@ !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Disallow words coming directly from root.
!! 
!! Use the following flag diacritics to control downcasing of derived proper
!! nouns (e.g. Finnish Pariisi -> pariisilainen). See e.g. North SГЎmi for how to use
!! these flags. There exists a ready-made regex that will do the actual down-casing
!! given the proper use of these flags.
!!
!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | ---- | -----------
@U.Cap.Obl@        !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Allowing downcasing of derived names
@U.Cap.Opt@        !!вүҲ |  @CODE@ | Allowing downcasing of derived names


